WEBVTT

00:05:29.167 --> 00:05:31.018
So said Dr. Yoti,

00:05:31.042 --> 00:05:34.684
a Ugandan doctor who worked for WHO

00:05:34.708 --> 00:05:37.643
and who had been involved
in pretty much every Ebola outbreak

00:05:37.667 --> 00:05:39.559
in Africa previously.

00:05:39.583 --> 00:05:40.893
He was right,

00:05:40.917 --> 00:05:44.125
and yet there was no plan
to make that happen.

00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:48.393
So during a weekend in early December,

00:05:48.417 --> 00:05:53.434
I developed a plan that became known
as the Western Area Surge plan.

00:05:53.458 --> 00:05:56.351
We needed to talk with people,

00:05:56.375 --> 00:05:58.059
not at people.

00:05:58.083 --> 00:06:02.143
We needed to work
with the community influencers